    "online": "京东商城:http://book.360buy.com/10010786.html 当当网:http://product.dangdang.com/main/product.aspx?product_id=22885907 亚马逊:http://www.amazon.cn/%E8%9B%99%E8%8E%AB%E8%A8%80%E8%91%972012%E8%AF%BA%E8%B4%9D%E5%B0%94%E6%96%87%E5%AD%A6%E5%A5%96%E8%8E%AB%E8%A8%80/dp/B009QX93SW 苏宁易购:http://www.suning.com/emall/prd_10052_22001_7_3315159_.html",
